trans-unit.source: Each key is tracked and a maximum 200 unique keys can be provided per AppInsights ikey (app).

trans-unit.source: Each property is initially classified as a dimension, enabling segmentation features based on each property's value set.
trans-unit.target: Each property is initially classified as a dimension, enabling segmentation features based on each property's value set.

trans-unit.source: Each value set is tracked per property key for its cardinality.
trans-unit.target: Each value set is tracked per property key for its cardinality.

trans-unit.source: When cardinality of a key exceeds 100 unique values, the property is classified as an attribute.
trans-unit.target: When cardinality of a key exceeds 100 unique values, the property is classified as an attribute.
